```
ERROR: Skipping '//tensorflow/core/platform/aws/...': no targets found beneath 'tensorflow/core/platform/aws'.
ERROR: Skipping '//tensorflow/core-platform/cloud/...': no targets found beneath 'tensorflow/core-platform/cloud'.

```
So lets modify the last line of your command, looking at our folders in the git repo, like this:
```

```
